Actually, I have a guess about what might be the problem here. How about changing
```scala
flatMap(_.scalaArgs.collectFirst { case Function(ValDef(_, a, _, _) :: Nil, b) => a -> c.resetLocalAttrs(b) }).
```

to 
```scala
